# iMessage channel: bridge posts to this server; credentials are in the bridge. Server host/port only.
# Core connection: use channels/.env (core_host, core_port, CORE_API_KEY).
# Copy to .env and set values if you need to override defaults.

# Optional: host/port this channel listens on (default 8012 / 0.0.0.0)
# IMESSAGE_CHANNEL_HOST=0.0.0.0
# IMESSAGE_CHANNEL_PORT=8012
